{
  "text": "The formula for double ramification cycles in [CITATION_1] and [JPPZ18] are obtained by relating it to certain Hurwitz-Hodge cycles which are also polynomials in r and the constant terms coincide with the constant terms of P d,r \u0393 (D, L). In Section 4, we generalize the identity between Hurwitz-Hodge cycles and double ramification cycles. As a direct consequence, HurwitzHodge cycles satisfy a refined polynomiality (see Corollary 4.2) which implies the vanishing theorem for P ",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "78089766"
